</div>

<div class="help-intro card">
  <p>Welcome to the <strong>Onassis Timeline</strong>, a research tool for documenting the life and events of Aristotle Onassis. This guide will help you understand how to effectively use the system to track your research from books, newspapers, and other sources.</p>
</div>

